<flag key="CLIENTS" name="Affects Players" bit="0">Give players a warning to return to the map</flag>
<flag key="NPCS" name="Affects NPCs" bit="1">Might affect AI Minions &amp; Titans; need to test with navmeshes</flag>
<flag key="BOTS" name="Disallow Bots" bit="12">Tell AI to stay out of here?</flag>
-------- NOTES --------
CLIENTS spawnflag must be set
</group>

